title: HelloHero: One-Pot Chermoula Prawns Pilaf with Yoghurt & Crushed Peanuts
description: One-pot cooking isn’t just convenient, it’s also full of lots of lovely flavours as everything comes together. Take a beef and prawn veggie pilaf, the Moroccan and chermoula spices melt in the bowl. One irresistible and easy dinner coming right up!

